<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>

<head>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
            line-height: 1.6;
            color: #333;
        }

        .container {
            max-width: 600px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            padding: 20px;
        }

        .header {
            background-color: #d1e7dd;
            padding: 20px;
            text-align: center;
            border-bottom: 3px solid #198754;
        }

        .content {
            padding: 20px;
        }

        .plan {
            font-size: 20px;
            font-weight: bold;
            color: #198754;
        }

        .details {
            background-color: #f8f9fa;
            padding: 15px;
            border-radius: 5px;
            margin: 20px 0;
        }

        .footer {
            text-align: center;
            font-size: 12px;
            color: #666;
            margin-top: 20px;
        }
    </style>
</head>

<body>
    <div class="container">
        <div class="header">
            <h2>Welcome to {{plan_name}}!</h2>
        </div>
        <div class="content">
            <p>Hello,</p>
            <p>Thank you for subscribing to the <span class="plan">{{plan_name}}</span> plan.</p>

            <div class="details">
                <p>Start Date: {{start_date}}</p>
                <p>Billing Cycle: {{interval}}</p>
                <p>Next Payment: {{next_payment_date}}</p>
            </div>

            <p>You now have access to all the features included in your plan. Visit your dashboard to get started.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="footer">
            <p>Â© {{year}} Oxidly. All rights reserved.</p>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>

</html>